- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possibility as the paper mentions the use of an interior point method, which is a common optimization technique in machine learning. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possibility as the paper proposes an algorithm for solving the scheduling problem, which can be considered an AI problem. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper deals with formulating the scheduling problem as a mathematical program.
